Class Bed

  • java.lang.Object
    • decoworld.model.world.safehouse.furniture.Bed

  • public class Bed
extends java.lang.Object
    This will store a player's bed inside their safehouse and the properties for it. Invariant: price >= 0 0 < comfort <= 10, 0 < size <= 10 user != null, user is a valid user in the game
